By using setInterval(handleProgressBar, 1000), the handleProgressBar function will be called every 1000 milliseconds (1 second). This allows the progress bar to dynamically update and display the elapsed time in seconds.
Without calling handleProgressBar periodically, the progress bar would not update, and the user would not see the updated time in seconds.

